data.text:
X-press mart is a retail brand that specializes in convenience store operations. It offers a wide range of products, including groceries, snacks, beverages, personal care items, and household essentials. With its convenient locations and quick service, X-press mart aims to provide customers with a hassle-free shopping experience.

X-press mart was established in 2005 as a small convenience store chain.

Over the years, the brand expanded its presence and opened more locations in different cities and regions.

X-press mart focuses on delivering quality products and excellent customer service.

The brand has developed a strong reputation for its convenient operating hours and strategic store placements.
